  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Services performed by the Contractor or its personnel under the terms of the contract."&lt;SEP&gt;"Services under the Contract are activities performed by Persons that may be restricted if disqualifying offenses are found."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Awarded Respondent must ensure quality in any other activity related to the administration of services under the contract."&lt;SEP&gt;"The services performed under the contract are prohibited from being conducted outside the U.S."</data>
