<node id="&quot;EMPLOYEES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Employees are individuals working under the Contractor."&lt;SEP&gt;"Employees of the Awarded Respondent are required to provide documentation and testimony as part of the review or appeal process."&lt;SEP&gt;"Employees of the Awarded Respondent must be available."&lt;SEP&gt;"Employees of the Contractor are included in the prohibition and must not perform services outside the U.S."&lt;SEP&gt;"Employees of the Contractor are individuals working under the Contractor."&lt;SEP&gt;"Employees of the Contractor are responsible for performing services and can contribute to liability if they fail to perform accurately."&lt;SEP&gt;"Employees of the Contractor may be rejected and barred from facilities for cause."&lt;SEP&gt;"Employees of the Contractor must undergo criminal background screening."&lt;SEP&gt;"Individuals employed by the Contractor who are subject to screening."&lt;SEP&gt;"Individuals working for the Contractor who are covered under the bond’s protection."&lt;SEP&gt;"Individuals working for the Department who are protected under the indemnification clause."&lt;SEP&gt;"The representatives must be employees, not subcontractors or temporary personnel."&lt;SEP&gt;"The workers employed by Subcontractors who must be covered by workers' compensation insurance."&lt;SEP&gt;"Workers performing work under the contract who are not protected by Workers' Compensation statutes and require additional insurance."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-5f9ddff393a5a6ceeb66f094e647f7fa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-929f90597b1751dba1a9fd1a32b051bc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-973e4e5caf2d5df7a31230aa09be9f8d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6e76ed74a8f332bb4b0ce48da988e36a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-adf38bec4792e1237dac8580ddd00b04&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8d64fe1d6f1d848dfb8c74c71b18155&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e260eaaa7468bbb26e412849c414e7b6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-973b86edc6f84e59f50507a111e8afca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7be865cd763682914359f37abc6f55c3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7e186e17653b287e3cfa5f205a6520f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c29476b54ecf1664862eece0459c63e6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b5a9d5f35482c8cebfb35f593b3063da</data>
