<node id="&quot;SUBCONTRACTORS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Entities working under the Contractor, also required to comply with cooperation obligations."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subcontractors are entities used by the Contractor to provide Services, and their acts or omissions are the responsibility of the Contractor."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subcontractors are not allowed to represent the Awarded Respondent at Benefit Fairs."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subcontractors are organizations working under the Contractor."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subcontractors are prohibited from performing services outside the U.S. or transmitting Florida Data abroad."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subcontractors are subject to audits by the Department for activities related to this Contract."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subcontractors are third parties hired by the Contractor to perform specific tasks."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subcontractors are third parties providing services under the Awarded Respondent."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subcontractors of the Contractor may be rejected and barred from facilities for cause."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subcontractors performing work under the Contract must comply with Department security and administrative requirements."&lt;SEP&gt;"Third parties hired by the Contractor to assist in service delivery."&lt;SEP&gt;"Third parties hired by the Contractor who must also provide workers' compensation insurance for their employees."&lt;SEP&gt;"Third parties working under the Contractor, also subject to audit and inspection."&lt;SEP&gt;"Third-party entities hired by the Contractor to perform part of the contract work, subject to screening."&lt;SEP&gt;"Third-party organizations that must also use E-Verify for their newly hired employees."&lt;SEP&gt;"Third-party organizations working under the Contractor, whose negligence can trigger liability."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-7be865cd763682914359f37abc6f55c3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-929f90597b1751dba1a9fd1a32b051bc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c767c42c4e19b535729414ef8d73ee8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-973e4e5caf2d5df7a31230aa09be9f8d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8484f7b881e4e7cbe9759b6862d56796&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0e6bf92f0ea1c6258861ff1086796ace&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-87aacb2e5a1d425f139e7028172e5302&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8d64fe1d6f1d848dfb8c74c71b18155&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e260eaaa7468bbb26e412849c414e7b6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-973b86edc6f84e59f50507a111e8afca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d4223fbc24b29d99308c28ad9b7af66&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f96bc837864e7d2f0162d851756dde37&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7e186e17653b287e3cfa5f205a6520f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b5a9d5f35482c8cebfb35f593b3063da</data>
