  <data key="d3">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Access to all Physicians is anticipated not to be achieved, despite the Contractor's efforts."&lt;SEP&gt;"Access to all Physicians is not expected to be achieved, as per the Department's anticipation."&lt;SEP&gt;"Participating physicians are healthcare providers who deliver services under the plan."&lt;SEP&gt;"Physicians are healthcare providers whose access is being discussed in the context of network maintenance and performance indicators."&lt;SEP&gt;"Physicians are individuals who are the subject of access provisions in the contract. The Department anticipates that access to all Physicians will not be achieved."&lt;SEP&gt;"Physicians employed by the Awarded Respondent may be called upon to provide testimony for Department's review or appeal."&lt;SEP&gt;"Physicians of the Awarded Respondent must be available."&lt;SEP&gt;"Physicians who are not demonstrating quality are contacted by the Associate Medical Director."</data>
