<node id="&quot;SERVICES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"ACTION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Services are authorized after benefits and eligibility are verified."&lt;SEP&gt;"Services are part of the deliverables and are provided by the Contractor."&lt;SEP&gt;"Services are tasks or work required under the Contract."&lt;SEP&gt;"Services are the tasks or work provided by the Contractor and its Subcontractors during the contract term."&lt;SEP&gt;"Services are the tasks to be performed by the Contractor as specified in the Contract, including all Deliverables and any inherent services required for proper delivery. The Department may add or delete services during the Contract term, requiring a negotiated amendment."&lt;SEP&gt;"Services are the work that Contractor is not allowed to subcontract without approval."&lt;SEP&gt;"Services required by the ITN and subsequent contract must be maintained at required proficiency."&lt;SEP&gt;"Services will commence on the Effective Date and end December 31, 2026."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Contractor must provide Services as described in the Contract in Region 2."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Contractor needs data to provide the Services."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Contractor performs Services under the Contract."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Contractor shall not perform Services after termination, except for continued portions."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Department may suspend any or all Services under the Contract."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Services are the deliverables or tasks the Contractor is required to perform under the contract."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Services are the required tasks under the contract that the Contractor must provide."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Services are the tasks or work required by the contract that the Contractor must perform accurately."&lt;SEP&gt;"The offerings within the disease management program, which are currently not provided."&lt;SEP&gt;"The services provided by the Contractor to the State under the contract."&lt;SEP&gt;"The services provided by the Contractor under the Contract."&lt;SEP&gt;"The work to be performed under the contract."&lt;SEP&gt;"Work or deliverables provided by the Contractor under the Contract."</data>
