<node id="&quot;ITN&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"DOCUMENT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A document (likely an Invitation to Negotiate) that required the Contractor to represent its business organization."&lt;SEP&gt;"A document or process (likely a Request for Proposal or similar) that awards regions to Respondents."&lt;SEP&gt;"ITN refers to a contractual or procedural document that governs the relationship and obligations of the Awarded Respondent."&lt;SEP&gt;"ITN refers to an event that results in contract termination, triggering data transfer obligations."&lt;SEP&gt;"The 16-month period follows the termination of the Contract resulting from this ITN."&lt;SEP&gt;"The ITN refers to a document that outlines required services."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Invitation to Negotiate (ITN) is a document requiring responses based on the specified benefit design."&lt;SEP&gt;"The contract termination resulting from this ITN triggers the 16-month post-termination meeting period."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-5c4a9169533286ec9e7cbfc255165a4b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-756bf9cd6cba13a690d1a1ab1ca15ac8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2800a47e9bda55f14b649f4433087f95&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9d8bc7fada8f87797f63efcdf326ef70&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-87aacb2e5a1d425f139e7028172e5302&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dd1ed5d9ddc784a0f14b59a08c792ef1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e260eaaa7468bbb26e412849c414e7b6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c767c42c4e19b535729414ef8d73ee8</data>
</node>
