<node id="&quot;STATE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A governmental entity responsible for overseeing compliance with federal and state laws, including HIPAA."&lt;SEP&gt;"The State conducts studies or surveys to evaluate compliance with the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"The State has the authority to conduct performance and compliance audits of the Awarded Respondent."&lt;SEP&gt;"The State has the right to retain funds from the Contractor to satisfy claims."&lt;SEP&gt;"The State imposes taxes or assessments."&lt;SEP&gt;"The State is a governmental entity that establishes policies for business participation in state contracts."&lt;SEP&gt;"The State is an entity that seeks to benefit from improvements in premium pricing during the contract period."&lt;SEP&gt;"The State is an organization that does not deem the Contractor or its personnel as employees."&lt;SEP&gt;"The State is represented by the Account Management Team to advance its best interests."&lt;SEP&gt;"The State is the entity that owns the Contract and has the right to receive it upon termination."&lt;SEP&gt;"The State is the entity that pays compensation directly to the Awarded Respondent."&lt;SEP&gt;"The State is the entity whose best interests the Account Management Team is obligated to advance."&lt;SEP&gt;"The State is the overarching governmental entity of which the Department is an agency."&lt;SEP&gt;"The State is the party that holds the Contractor accountable for performance and is protected against losses due to failure to perform."&lt;SEP&gt;"The State may face offsets due to failure in resolving Medicare Secondary payer notices."&lt;SEP&gt;"The State owns all claim records, data elements, and eligibility data related to the contract."&lt;SEP&gt;"The State refers to the State of Florida."&lt;SEP&gt;"The broader governmental entity protected by the bond, alongside the Department."&lt;SEP&gt;"The governmental entity that procures services and may contract with multiple vendors."&lt;SEP&gt;"The state government entity whose employees are restricted from being employed by the Contractor."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-5f9ddff393a5a6ceeb66f094e647f7fa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5c4a9169533286ec9e7cbfc255165a4b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-63f578d53bfa5cd1841300ebfaf269bc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-756bf9cd6cba13a690d1a1ab1ca15ac8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c767c42c4e19b535729414ef8d73ee8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-973e4e5caf2d5df7a31230aa09be9f8d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6e76ed74a8f332bb4b0ce48da988e36a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-87aacb2e5a1d425f139e7028172e5302&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dd1ed5d9ddc784a0f14b59a08c792ef1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-adf38bec4792e1237dac8580ddd00b04&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8d64fe1d6f1d848dfb8c74c71b18155&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d72ea75fb519c8242ca877027c6dc469&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2ac2c9a651e12d0bbc80acf2a9565c92&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fb25811043bde746cec405019a7c28d2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8484f7b881e4e7cbe9759b6862d56796&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3a27bbe9186e0b89c85dff042c6e2c65&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ced7b0d6c3e25b1f766368ff30d9f7db</data>
</node>
