<node id="&quot;PERSON&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A Person is an individual who may have a criminal misdemeanor or felony record and is subject to removal from access to State of Florida Data or contract services."&lt;SEP&gt;"A human individual who may or may not be approved to participate in the Contract."&lt;SEP&gt;"A person includes their authorized successors and assigns."&lt;SEP&gt;"A person refers to any individual, including employees, agents, or subcontractors, who must be screened before performing services or accessing data."&lt;SEP&gt;"An individual who may be disqualified if found to have a criminal misdemeanor."&lt;SEP&gt;"An individual who may not be employed, subcontracted with, or sub-granted to by the Contractor if they are employed by the State or involved in the Contract’s performance."&lt;SEP&gt;"Each Person must undergo background screening that is refreshed every five years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Person refers to any individual operating under the Contractor’s direction who performs services under the Contract."</data>
