<node id="&quot;STATE OF FLORIDA DATA&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"DATA"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Access to State of Florida Data must be secure and compliant with the Contract and applicable rules."&lt;SEP&gt;"Data owned or managed by the State of Florida, which requires access control and screening."&lt;SEP&gt;"Data that is subject to breach or incident reporting."&lt;SEP&gt;"Data that must be protected from further unauthorized access."&lt;SEP&gt;"Personal information stored in electronic form that is subject to breach."&lt;SEP&gt;"Sensitive or official data belonging to the State of Florida, which must be preserved and recreated if lost due to negligence."&lt;SEP&gt;"State of Florida Data is a specific category of data defined in section 1 of the contract, likely referring to data owned or managed by the State of Florida."&lt;SEP&gt;"State of Florida Data is a specific category of data defined in the contract, including all forms such as digital, physical, in transit, or in memory, and includes metadata."&lt;SEP&gt;"State of Florida Data is sensitive information that may be accessed directly or indirectly by Persons performing services."&lt;SEP&gt;"State of Florida Data is sensitive information that requires access control and is protected under the contract."&lt;SEP&gt;"State of Florida Data must not be disclosed to any unauthorized person or entity not directly approved to participate in the contract."&lt;SEP&gt;"State of Florida Data refers to sensitive information belonging to the State of Florida that must be secured by the Contractor."&lt;SEP&gt;"State of Florida Data refers to sensitive information belonging to the State of Florida, which must not be sent, transmitted, or accessed outside the U.S."&lt;SEP&gt;"State of Florida Data refers to sensitive personal information protected under Florida law."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-7be865cd763682914359f37abc6f55c3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-929f90597b1751dba1a9fd1a32b051bc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e9b2fbc62ea8c019a8196a95956dc5b2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d03da7ad0a2c45bd8acfaa3e7086933e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-042bc330a3f245f87e013cf42b730533&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7009d4e99c1b1b5f2db7b0b27c5aab50&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-973b86edc6f84e59f50507a111e8afca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f27e3efb4e453bfd444a2596a8c9623f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f96bc837864e7d2f0162d851756dde37&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b5a9d5f35482c8cebfb35f593b3063da</data>
</node>
