  <data key="d3">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A Breach is an incident involving unauthorized access to State of Florida Data."&lt;SEP&gt;"A breach of the subsection leads to damages that are difficult to ascertain."&lt;SEP&gt;"A breach refers to an incident involving unauthorized access or disclosure of confidential personal information."&lt;SEP&gt;"A confirmed event compromising confidentiality, integrity, or availability of State of Florida Data."&lt;SEP&gt;"A confirmed event compromising confidentiality, integrity, or availability of information or State of Florida Data."&lt;SEP&gt;"A confirmed event that compromises confidentiality, integrity, or availability of information or State of Florida Data, or unauthorized access to electronic State of Florida Data containing personal information."</data>
