<node id="&quot;SECTION 7.3&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONTRACTUAL PROVISION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Section 7.3 is a contractual provision that allows the Department to act upon the Contractor's good faith effort, functioning as a performance guarantee."&lt;SEP&gt;"Section 7.3 is a contractual provision that grants the Department the right to take action upon the Contractor's good faith effort to meet access criteria. It is treated as a performance guarantee."&lt;SEP&gt;"Section 7.3 is a performance guarantee that the Department may exercise under specified conditions."&lt;SEP&gt;"Section 7.3 is a performance guarantee that the Department may invoke upon good faith effort by the Contractor."&lt;SEP&gt;"Section 7.3 is a provision that the Department is not obligated to exercise."&lt;SEP&gt;"Section 7.3 is not mandatory for the Department to exercise, despite the Contractor's efforts."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-112e64f1bb6118d9bccd195e08f5f314&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-536bb3f69282f0b1683044e52fc49ca7</data>
