<node id="&quot;ID CARDS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"OBJECT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"ID Cards are to be mailed by the Awarded Respondent to all Participants, excluding Social Security Numbers, and must be sent by the earlier of December 15, 2023, or ten business days after receiving a clean and accurate Open Enrollment eligibility file."&lt;SEP&gt;"ID cards are mailed to new members after clean eligibility and enrollment files are received, with a target of 99.0% completion within 4 business days."&lt;SEP&gt;"ID cards are physical or digital cards issued to subscribers for identification and access to benefits."&lt;SEP&gt;"ID cards may be mailed with a customized greeting and form letter."&lt;SEP&gt;"Identification cards issued to Plan Participants."&lt;SEP&gt;"Identification cards to be mailed to participants."&lt;SEP&gt;"Maintenance ID Cards are physical cards issued to eligible persons, processed and mailed based on eligibility files."&lt;SEP&gt;"Physical cards issued to participants that display a unique Participant-identifying number and must comply with State standards."&lt;SEP&gt;"Physical or digital cards issued to participants to verify their health plan membership, generated using the Open Enrollment file."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-2800a47e9bda55f14b649f4433087f95&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b57b1f6f75687090fceb29727cfad251&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dc984120e1f1f604e806000ba1bb8141&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cebd27b76b8ffb6789a18f25f37456f7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9006c08df8e9a1ab15da5260fb57b4d1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c9aaa428a9cedb15e5c65db44f369179&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-be8d8979403f6066066c55d416f7a095&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ced7b0d6c3e25b1f766368ff30d9f7db</data>
