<node id="&quot;PLAN&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A health or benefits plan administered by the Awarded Respondent for participants."&lt;SEP&gt;"A program or system administered by Contractor."&lt;SEP&gt;"A program or system related to benefits or services, subject to legal actions or proceedings."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Plan is a benefits program that includes specific coverages, products, and materials."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Plan is a healthcare or insurance program for which claim-related data must be provided by the Awarded Respondent."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Plan is a structured program administered by the Department and subject to legal and administrative proceedings."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Plan is a system or program related to the Awarded Respondent's operations."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Plan is the entity for which financial and statistical data is reported."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Plan is the program or service for which complaints are being reported."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Plan is the service being evaluated in the satisfaction survey."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Plan refers to a healthcare or benefits program administered under the Department’s oversight, covering services such as retail, mail, specialty pharmacy, and Medicare secondary drugs and supplies."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Plan will not be administered under this Contract until January 1, 2024."&lt;SEP&gt;"The netting of payments related to the Plan is prohibited."&lt;SEP&gt;"The plan associated with the Contract, which may be impacted by Changes."&lt;SEP&gt;"The plan is a healthcare service framework under which the Respondent operates."&lt;SEP&gt;"The plan refers to a healthcare service plan under which hospitals provide services."&lt;SEP&gt;"The plan refers to a healthcare service plan under which physicians provide services."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-5c4a9169533286ec9e7cbfc255165a4b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-756bf9cd6cba13a690d1a1ab1ca15ac8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-112e64f1bb6118d9bccd195e08f5f314&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b57b1f6f75687090fceb29727cfad251&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-db666e270f96718db00f123739d57c9c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a21de729aeac2ac5411293b5eb7a85b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-42eb7824bc4b6dae1f55110a76cae692&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fb8c857dfc2485b3c018e2a6930093e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a15086157f2c790665924983ad25ad5f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7b254c4b63c9acf3eabfaab008c51ce0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7afb47b665f9a355360d8f19b072515d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8d64fe1d6f1d848dfb8c74c71b18155&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-74cef71ea7584b44187a4071e42aec9b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-86d51fd3dc4466f1769637ccb655bea2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-634b420b1dffb2db682f1098aa431f4e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c29476b54ecf1664862eece0459c63e6</data>
