</node>
<node id="&quot;DATA&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"OBJECT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Data is any information that can be reviewed, inspected, accessed, stored, retrieved, transmitted, or otherwise used, regardless of type, form, or storage method."&lt;SEP&gt;"Data is defined in section 1 of the contract and may include any information collected, stored, or processed under the agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"Data refers to any representation of information, knowledge, facts, concepts, computer software, or programs, including confidential, exempt, or protected health information under HIPAA, HITECH Act, or Florida Statutes."&lt;SEP&gt;"Information provided by the Awarded Respondent to support the Department’s instant responses."&lt;SEP&gt;"Information required by the Department to respond to public records and subpoenas, provided by the Awarded Respondent."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Contractor must make all requested data available for audits."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-0d4223fbc24b29d99308c28ad9b7af66&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-929f90597b1751dba1a9fd1a32b051bc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b57b1f6f75687090fceb29727cfad251&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-042bc330a3f245f87e013cf42b730533</data>
</node>
