</node>
<node id="&quot;ACCOUNT MANAGEMENT TEAM&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"TEAM"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A department within the Awarded Respondent responsible for managing participant accounts and supporting legislative responses."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Account Management Team acts on behalf of the State to advance the State's best interests through the Awarded Respondent's corporate structure."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Account Management Team has an organizational chart that must be kept current."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Account Management Team is a dedicated group assigned by the Awarded Respondent, including an executive sponsor, account director/executive, account manager, customer service manager, data/fiscal analyst, and medical director, and is responsible for managing services under the Contract."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Account Management Team is subject to two annual Performance Reviews conducted by the Department."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Account Management Team must attend all quarterly meetings at the State offices in Tallahassee, Florida."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Account Management Team must be thoroughly familiar with the Awarded Respondent's functions and operations related to the Department and the Plan."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Account Management Team must devote time and resources to manage the State account and be available for telephonic, email, and on-site consultations."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-756bf9cd6cba13a690d1a1ab1ca15ac8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b57b1f6f75687090fceb29727cfad251&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ced7b0d6c3e25b1f766368ff30d9f7db</data>
</node>
