  <data key="d4">"Implementation Date is January 1, 2024, at 12:00 A.M., Eastern Time (EST)."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Implementation Date is January 1, 2024, at 12:00 A.M. Eastern Time, when the contract or its provisions are to be implemented."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Implementation Date is the date from which Darrell Gholar is designated as the Department's Contract Manager."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Implementation Date is the deadline by which readiness assessments are conducted."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Implementation Date is the deadline by which the program must be satisfactorily installed."&lt;SEP&gt;"The date when a corrective action is scheduled to be implemented."&lt;SEP&gt;"The date when the plan goes live, which is January 1, 2024."&lt;SEP&gt;"The implementation date is January 1, 2024, at 12:00:00 A.M., a critical deadline for the Awarded Respondent to achieve full operational status."&lt;SEP&gt;"The implementation date of each corrective action must be specified."&lt;SEP&gt;"The official start date of the plan, January 1, 2024, at 12:00:00 A.M."</data>
