  <data key="d3">"DOCUMENT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A plan detailing the steps and milestones for implementing the benefits program."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Implementation Plan contains the deadlines that must be met."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Implementation Plan is a final plan with tasks and deliverable dates required to install the program by the Implementation Date."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Implementation Plan is a schedule approved by the Department outlining service delivery timelines."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Implementation Plan is a written description provided by the Contractor and approved by the Department, detailing the schedule of actions to implement services and fulfill the Contract in a timely manner."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Implementation Plan is a written description provided by the Contractor outlining how the contract will be implemented."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Implementation Plan must be satisfactory to the Department."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Implementation Plan must be submitted to the Department for approval."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Implementation Plan must be submitted to the Department."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Implementation Plan must detail all steps for full performance."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Implementation Plan must detail all steps to begin full performance of the Contract."</data>
