<node id="&quot;PARTIES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Both the Department and the Contractor are considered Parties to the Contract."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Parties are entities that must cooperate fully in administrative or legal proceedings initiated by Plan Enrollees or other persons related to the Plan or Contract."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Parties are the Department and the Contractor, who wish to avoid litigation."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Parties are the Department and the Contractor."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Parties are the entities agreeing to the contract."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Parties are the entities that sign and agree to the contract, making it legally binding."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Parties refer to the Contractor and the Department, who acknowledge the nature of liquidated damages."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Parties refer to the Contractor and the Department, who must mutually agree to suspend Performance Guarantees."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Parties refer to the Contractor and the Department."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Parties refer to the Department and the Contractor, who may jointly issue a press release."&lt;SEP&gt;"The State and the Contractor, collectively."&lt;SEP&gt;"The term 'Parties' collectively refers to the State of Florida, Department of Management Services and Capital Health Plan, Inc., the two entities involved in the contract."&lt;SEP&gt;"The two main entities involved in the Contract: Contractor and Department."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-79a76389ae9d41ad98c308997796bb27&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-973e4e5caf2d5df7a31230aa09be9f8d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2bb11a44dfb0a8eaa9a9252f491073e6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8d64fe1d6f1d848dfb8c74c71b18155&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eaa3b36fea58d72059cd585dada27264&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bb21fd01b6cf2ffac2e48390b9e584cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-042bc330a3f245f87e013cf42b730533&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-973b86edc6f84e59f50507a111e8afca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c767c42c4e19b535729414ef8d73ee8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a7c62733ea576c9deceb35110683bdd8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3a27bbe9186e0b89c85dff042c6e2c65&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7b254c4b63c9acf3eabfaab008c51ce0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-80197926c45627b0efe3aa47310d15c0</data>
